### User Register
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName" : "abhi",
    "lastName" : "kk",
    "email" : "a@gmail.com",
    "password" : "123",
    "profileImageUrl" : "http://example.com/avatar.png"
}



### login user
POST  http://localhost:4000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email" : "a@gmail.com",
    "password" : "123"
}



### read all articles for user
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/user




### add comments to an article
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users-comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "uid" : "69aeeaa0a54ded8516c4ea94",
    "articleId" : "69aee3b90251a40e36443ba3",
    "comment" : "Can do better broooo..."
}





