### read articles from author (protected)
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69afca09faa1f81ee460a067


### Update article
PATCH http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author": "69ae92141b905bf3821f53d3",
    "articleId" : "69aee3b90251a40e36443ba3",
    "title": "Bhalu",
    "category" : "comedy",
    "content": "sdjvbskdjv ksjdvbsdjbv "
}


### delete article (soft)
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles-delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "authorId": "69afca09faa1f81ee460a067",
    "articleId" : "69c66a12f0452b0edfb4380a"
}


### restore article
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/article-reload
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "authorId": "69afca09faa1f81ee460a067",
    "articleId" : "69c66a12f0452b0edfb4380a"
}


###logout
GET http://localhost:4000/common-api/logout





